                                         using s                      .
           move      s-dat                to   w-det-qta-orc-dat      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   det-qta-orc-000      thru det-qta-orc-999        .
