                     rf-ofr-num-mag       not  = w-det-qta-orf-cod
                     go to det-qta-orf-999.
       det-qta-orf-140.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezione sul record                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
