                     go to rpd-rof-ric-999.
       rpd-rof-ric-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Indicatore di programma in esecuzione           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "IE"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Read Next su [bfr]                              *
